Star Conflicts is a new turn-based space strategy and tactical game for iOS! 

Meet the outstanding graphics and easy controls. 
Enjoy an exciting adventure through the galaxy as a captain of the motorized Space Marines. 
Play the interesting story missions and visit many locations. 
Unlock new types of units and upgrade them. 
Pick up bonuses and use them during battle. 
Use all your strategic abilities, use the terrain tactical tricks to crush your enemies! 

Main features of the game: 
- Brilliant 3D graphics of space; 
- 5 challenging missions; 
- Difficulty levels from EASY to HARD; 
- 3 types of unique locations; 
- 6 types of combat units; 
- Unit upgrade system; 
- tactical terrain tricks and random events; 
- System of Achievements; 
- Available in English, Russian, Chinese, Portugal, Spanish, French, Korean, German.

